com.samskivert.util
Class DependencyGraph<T>

java.lang.Object
  com.samskivert.util.DependencyGraph<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of object maintained in the graph.
public class DependencyGraph<T>
extends Object

Maintains a bidirectional graph to manage the order that the items are removed. Children must wait until their parents are accessed - thus removing an available element means that a node without parents (an orphan) is removed and returned and the rest of the graph is updated to reflect that removal.
